  <title xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support to C40 Business Plan 2020-2024</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Accelerating climate action in large cities in developing countries</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The development objective is to contribute to resilient, low-carbon cities in developing countries through the reduction of greenhouse gas emissions, and, in particular, enhanced climate risk resilience and the promotion of building back better and greener from the Covid-19 crisis. The focus is on C40 member cities in low income and lower middle-income countries in Africa and Asia. 
Close collaboration is foreseen throughout the implementation through e.g. active engagement of relevant Danish embassies, secondment at senior technical level, and continued strategic dialogue.
The agreement includes indicators at impact and outcome level.</narrative>
  </description>
